title: Trophy Case Multi-Put Scoring (ADR-228 D4)
story: dungeo
description: Regression test for the live bug where "put all in case" deposited treasures without awarding trophy score (putting's multi-object path bypassed all interceptor hooks)

---

# Setup — grab two treasures via GDT and teleport to the trophy case
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT ready"]

> tk jeweled egg
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> tk canary
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> ah Living Room
[OK: contains "Teleported"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

> open case
[OK: contains "open"]

# ============================================================
# Test: put all in case — EVERY deposited treasure must award
# its trophy value (egg 5 + canary 2 = 7)
# ============================================================

> put all in case
[OK: contains "egg"]
[OK: contains "canary"]
[EVENT: true, type="if.event.put_in"]

> score
[OK: contains "7"]
